1
00:00:47,440 --> 00:00:48,300
A Rubik's cube.

2
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:52,200
Lady Cangyue, you know what this is?

3
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:57,180
How could there be such a thing in the palace?

4
00:00:57,680 --> 00:01:00,600
Eunuch Jingyuan provided the blueprint

5
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,800
for the young prince's new toy.

6
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:05,040
It's my first time seeing it too.

7
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:08,039
Jingyuan knows how to make modern toys.

8
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:09,840
Is he an experiencer too?

9
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:12,800
Impossible, Sister Xiaoyue.

10
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:34,039
Young Prince, you can't do this.

11
00:01:34,039 --> 00:01:35,960
What are you doing?

12
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:38,280
Young Prince, you can't do this.

13
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:42,000
Can I watch such R-rated plots?

14
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,039
Eunuch Sun.

15
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,920
Why do you smell

16
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:50,280
just like Auntie?

17
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,800
Grand Princess, Eunuch Sun.

18
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,720
A new clue has appeared.

19
00:01:58,440 --> 00:02:00,720
Why don't I have it?

20
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,680
This is a reward from His Majesty.

21
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,880
Uh, do you want it too, Young Prince?

22
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,480
No, it smells bad.

23
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,080
I want to go play with Sister Xiaoyue.

24
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,800
Sister Xiaoyue, let's go.

25
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,240
Oh no.

26
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,200
I'm exposed.

27
00:02:26,320 --> 00:02:28,200
The Young Prince knows.

28
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:30,180
Children say what they think.

29
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,360
I can explain.

30
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,800
If Cang Yue finds out,

31
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,640
His Majesty will find out.

32
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,320
If His Majesty finds out,

33
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,240
will I survive?

34
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:51,200
Cang Yue cannot be kept alive. She must die.

35
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:22,480
This palace maid must die.

36
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,960
But...

37
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,600
His Majesty likes her.

38
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:31,000
I can't let His Majesty know that I killed her.

39
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:33,360
Think of a way.

40
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,800
Eunuch, she's awake. She's awake.

41
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:41,320
Don't be afraid. We have nothing to hide.

42
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,680
Continue.

43
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,760
Eunuch Sun.

44
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,579
It seems this really is a new clue.

45
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,720
No matter what,

46
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,000
I must protect the last bloodline of the Yueyin tribe.

47
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:57,800
Your Majesty.

48
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,320
Didn't I tell you to call Cang Yue over?

49
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:01,000
Where is she?

50
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,400
Lady Cang Yue is missing.

51
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:03,520
We've searched everywhere,

52
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,280
but couldn't find her.

53
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:04,880
What?

54
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,240
However, a maid said

55
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:09,400
she saw Lady Cang Yue last go to the young prince's courtyard.

56
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:12,200
But she wasn't at the young prince's place either.

57
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,610
Go to Yuqing Palace.

58
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:14,240
Yes.

59
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,700
I got another idea.

60
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,200
How about poisoned wine?

61
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,880
Just one bowl and she'll die peacefully.

62
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,240
Poisoned wine?

63
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:27,400
Okay, let's use poisoned wine.

64
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,520
What if she's allergic to alcohol?

65
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:31,360
Get lost.

66
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,600
Are you allergic to alcohol?

67
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,960
Whatever, poisoned wine it is.

68
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,720
Go.

69
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,360
Go.

70
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,880
Sister Xiaoyue.

71
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:19,840
Ah.

72
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,440
You.

73
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:58,960
Where is Cang Yue?

74
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,280
Your Majesty,

75
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,920
she is your person.

76
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,780
Why would she be in Yuqing Palace?

77
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,960
Someone saw that

78
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,560
Lady Cang Yue came to

79
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,200
the young prince's place today.

80
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,520
Then I wouldn't know.

81
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,810
Bad news, Your Majesty!

82
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,360
The young prince is missing.

83
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,400
What did you say?

84
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:23,040
I... I know where the prince is.

85
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,280
Drink it.

86
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,360
I won't drink. I'm allergic to alcohol.

87
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,200
Drink!

88
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,440
No.

89
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:31,170
There's a sound over there.

90
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,440
Your Majesty.

91
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,600
Your Majesty.

92
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,330
Are you okay?

93
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,220
Your Highness.

94
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,440
Your Highness, are you okay?

95
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:45,640
Your Majesty,

96
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:50,200
I was almost beaten to death.

97
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,120
I don't know

98
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:55,840
how I offended Eunuch Sun

99
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,960
for him to be so ruthless.

100
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:01,400
Sun Liang, how dare you?

101
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,860
How dare you use lynching?

102
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:03,880
Your Majesty.

103
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:07,000
She clearly beat me.

104
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,400
Me?

105
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,960
Your Majesty, I'm just a weak woman.

106
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,640
How could I possibly beat the three of them?

107
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:18,320
Brother, I feel so dizzy.

108
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,000
Your Majesty.

109
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,960
The young prince has needle marks on him.

110
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:24,800
What?

111
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,560
How dare you, Sun Liang!

112
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,240
Not only did you plot against Cang Yue,

113
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,370
but you also dared to lay a hand on A Yan.

114
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:39,050
It wasn't me, Your Majesty.

115
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,880
It was these two young eunuchs.

116
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,610
I killed them for Your Majesty.

117
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:47,560
Si Xingxuan seems afraid to make a move against Eunuch Sun.

118
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,360
Could it be...

119
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,680
Eunuch Sun, why do you have

120
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:56,159
the same scent as Auntie?

121
00:07:57,920 --> 00:08:00,600
Is Eunuch Sun working for the Grand Princess?
